## What's Changed
* Support historic Rfy packet lenghts by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/143


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.29.2...0.30.0

## What's Changed
* Switch to full length rfy commands by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/141


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.29.1...0.29.2

## What's Changed
* Fix invalid RSSI byte used for TIC parsing. by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/142


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.29.0...0.29.1

## What's Changed
* Lint go green now by @Jamstah in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/137
* Add friendly names for tic by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/138
* Support for sending Funkbus commands by @AlainH in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/139
* Update Funkbus command names; Add Funkbus parse tests by @AlainH in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/140

## New Contributors
* @AlainH made their first contribution in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/139

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.28.0...0.29.0

## What's Changed
* Cleanup tests and linting by @Jamstah in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/131
* Add parsing for undecoded messages by @Jamstah in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/132
* Switch TFA rain sensor value by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/133
* Gh actions for test and lint by @Jamstah in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/135
* Support parsing TIC by @elupus in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/136

## New Contributors
* @Jamstah made their first contribution in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/131

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.27.1...0.28.0

## What's Changed
* Adding devices to RollerTrol by @tuxick in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/124
* Ignore packets with invalid length by @mbrrg in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/123
* Fix bug in sock.recv by @rhpijnacker in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/127

## New Contributors
* @tuxick made their first contribution in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/124
* @mbrrg made their first contribution in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/123
* @rhpijnacker made their first contribution in https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/pull/127

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Danielhiversen/pyRFXtrx/compare/0.27.0...0.27.1

## What’s Changed
* Add rain sensors support (#121) @elupus
* Add security device and make chime a standard command (#116) @elupus
* Fix send command for Lightning4 (#120) @RobBie1221
- #18 Added open, close and stop commands for Lighting5
